{"tid":1726614,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發！！！！！解放軍出動清場","createTime":"2019-11-16T08:33:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T10:13:20.000Z","uid":192226,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"b378bf57a0d82d80fee01a1465be564ae63ad0d2","tid":1726614,"uid":192226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:33:13.000Z","msg":"件衫寫住特戰八連清緊浸大rb <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BGaCoNj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBGaCoNj.png&h=c3c07cfb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"700c69477de445fa89ec17ff0e80c5d3a3ec5f42","tid":1726614,"uid":192226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:33:46.000Z","msg":"點搞"},{"pid":"bd834fb24e96f0cf43fc89317c879c2745cbbb65","tid":1726614,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:33:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a574eaae8a3cb98ae92c083dac3cd8a38d04ee2","tid":1726614,"uid":250511,"like":17,"dislike":4,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:34:05.000Z","msg":"睇到個標題嚇到叫左出黎，老細問咩事，我照讀比佢聽，讀左標題內文都未開始讀，佢成塊面白哂，自言自語，猛咁話「共慘黨殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生；共慘黨殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n跟住衝左上天台，叫左一聲「鳴呀，點解係我」就跳左落去，成班同事追上去都追唔切，有兩個女同事嚇到暈左，仲有個男同事當場嚇到變左弱智，不停問人要唔要食腸仔蛋。<br />\n<br />\n我就好好彩無咩事，但同班同事五十幾個人即時變左失業，你條仆街真係害人害物&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"5fa91116f381f75d900d2104174cafdaf651023b","tid":1726614,"uid":27416,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:34:45.000Z","msg":"屌你啲workrate <br />\n睇完hku 個邊好似加左速咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ede8a8d051484e322a1133aeab6d7cf3835feb","tid":1726614,"uid":266736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:35:11.000Z","msg":"解放軍可以行出街既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac7b3a0afcdf12c37beec313195d1eae50f17a9f","tid":1726614,"uid":192226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-